name: Water Dragon Cluster
desc: Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Must be Special Summoned with the effect of a "Bonding" Spell/Trap, and cannot be Special Summoned by other ways. If this card is Special Summoned: You can activate this effect; until the end of this turn, change the ATK of all Effect Monsters your opponent currently controls to 0, also they cannot activate their effects. You can Tribute this card (Quick Effect); Special Summon 2 copies of "Water Dragon" from your hand and/or Deck in Defense Position, ignoring their Summoning conditions.
